<HEADLINE> Vietnam's Power Grid Covers All Provinces </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HANOI, July 15 (Xinhua) -- Vietnam has made progress in power
industry with power grid coverage reaching all provinces of the
country.
</P>
<P>
Vietnam's electricity grid now covers all provinces of the
country with the connection last month of the northern mountainous
province of Lai Chau, according to a report of Vietnam's official
news agency VNA Saturday.
</P>
<P>
Vietnam has increased electricity production by almost 13
percent in the past 12 months, with production of nearly 13
billion kwh in the first six months of the year.
</P>
<P>
