been difficulties, particularly in delays bringing the new Yaly
and Hinh river hydro stations on stream.
</P>
<P>
Vietnam currently has 13 main power stations, seven are thermal
and the remainder are hydro-powered. Together they have a total
capacity of 5,500 mw and annually produce roughly 22-23 billion
kwh of power. 
