<HEADLINE> Hakkinen Takes Pole Position for Austrian Grand Prix </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
VIENNA, July 15 (Xinhua) -- MIka Hakkinen of McLaren-Mercedes
took his first pole position in three months as he led the way in
qualifying SAturday for the Austrian Grand Prix at Spielberg.
</P>
<P>
