of one minute 10.410 seconds around the 4.326-kilometer Al-Ring
circuit. His teammate David Coulthard was next with 1:10.795.
</P>
<P>
Rubens Barrichello and Michael Schumacher of Ferrari were third
and fourth respectively. Barrichello clocked 1:10.844 while
Schumacher was timed at 1:11.046. 
