up with investment in the country especially in the field of the
information technology, power and catering service sectors through
corporate system.
</P>
<P>
While expressing the willingness to invest in the country, the
BBCC Regional President Ahmed Samad Chowdhury pointed out that the
main problem is red-tapism which has in fact blocked the channel
of investment. 
