</P>
<P>
Joseph Borg, foreign minister of Malta, will pay an official
visit to China from July 20 to 27, at the invitation of Chinese
Foreign Minister Tang Jiaxuan.
</P>
<P>
 China welcomes Russia's New Diplomatic Concept
</P>
<P>
China welcomes Russia's new diplomatic concept to strengthen
relations with Asia, especially with China, Zhu said Thursday. (
more)
