</P>
<P>
The pilot did not report what was wrong with the fighter before
the crash, the third involving Polish MiG-21s since 1999, the
television station said. The report did not give the cause of the
accident, but said such MiG-21 jets in Poland are obsolete. Last
May, a Polish MiG-21 fighter crashed in northern Poland and its
pilot survived. Five months later, another Polish MiG-21 jet
crashed on the Baltic Coast shortly after its pilot ejected. (
