Laotian President's Visit to China:
</P>
<P>
Laotian President Arrives in Beijing
</P>
<P>
President of Laos Khamtay Siphandone and his party arrived in
Beijing Thursday for a three-day state visit to China.
</P>
<P>
Khamtay Siphandone is paying the visit at the invitation of
Chinese President Jiang Zemin.
</P>
<P>
Chinese, Laotian President Hold Talks
</P>
<P>
China and Laos will promote their cooperative relations in the
years to come, according to talks Friday between the presidents of
the two countries.
</P>
<P>
Chinese President Jiang Zemin said relations between the two
countries and parties have been developing well since the
normalization of bilateral relations 10 years ago and have yielded
positive results, and peace and stability in border area have
maintained.
</P>
<P>
