important to take steps as a matter of utmost urgency to put an
end to it," he said.
</P>
<P>
Mandela repeated that he had confidence in Mbeki and the ANC
leadership and the good judgment of the vast majority of the ANC's
members and South Africans.
</P>
<P>
"The ANC is on the march. There is no force in the country,
whatsoever, that can stop the ANC," he said. 
