Jorge Batlle, said he is convinced that all the members of the
Southern Common Market (Mercosur) -- Argentina, Brazil, Paraguay
and Uruguay -- are opposed to "the closing into itself of the
region, but that they want it to remain open to all the countries
of the hemisphere.
</P>
<P>
